name: BIOE 122L
title: Invertebrate Zoology Laboratory
description: An examination of invertebrates and their habitats. Weekly laboratories or field trips.

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): BIOL 20A, BIOE 20B, and BIOE 20C, and satisfaction of the Entry Level Writing and Composition requirements.

class_notes: Concurrent enrollment in BIOE 122 is required.
